                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "cv38JX0",
                  "fill": "#4B5563",
                  "content": "Principal Engineer with extensive experience delivering large-scale, customer-facing systems at Sky. Strong track record of leading complex initiatives, improving engineering standards, and driving cross-team collaboration. Skilled in React, TypeScript, GraphQL, Node.js and platform engineering. Known for rapid problem-solving, technical leadership, and the ability to stabilise and deliver projects under pressure. Committed to accessibility, security, and mentoring engineers across all levels.",
