                  "fontWeight": "bold"
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "cv67IsL",
                  "name": "role",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 6,
                  "padding": [
                    16,
                    0,
                    0,
                    0
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv60MyL",
                      "fill": "#111827",
                      "content": "Sky — Principal Engineer",
                      "fontFamily": "Lexend",
                      "fontSize": 18,
                      "fontWeight": "semibold"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv61ffi",
                      "fill": "#6B7280",
                      "content": "Dec 2022 – Present",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv62TFS",
                      "fill": "#4B5563",
                      "content": "• Provided technical leadership across multiple teams delivering customer service and CRM platforms.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv63KPp",
                      "fill": "#4B5563",
                      "content": "• Led platform-wide initiatives to improve accessibility, security, and developer experience.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv64woH",
                      "fill": "#4B5563",
                      "content": "• Acted as first responder for critical security incidents, rapidly diagnosing and mitigating high-severity threats.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv65okA",
                      "fill": "#4B5563",
                      "content": "• Drove architectural improvements across React and GraphQL services, including the new AI‑integrated SkyGate layer.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv66hju",
                      "fill": "#4B5563",
                      "content": "• Supported engineers across the organisation through mentoring, code reviews, and community-building.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "cv73fXy",
                  "name": "role",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 6,
                  "padding": [
                    16,
                    0,
                    0,
                    0
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv68Szk",
                      "fill": "#111827",
                      "content": "Sky — Tech Lead",
                      "fontFamily": "Lexend",
                      "fontSize": 18,
                      "fontWeight": "semibold"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv69rWB",
                      "fill": "#6B7280",
                      "content": "Apr 2021 – Jan 2023",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv70SSq",
                      "fill": "#4B5563",
                      "content": "• Led feature teams delivering major components of Sky's CRM and digital sales platforms.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv71vaU",
                      "fill": "#4B5563",
                      "content": "• Guided technical design, prioritisation, and delivery across multi-team initiatives.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv72U57",
                      "fill": "#4B5563",
                      "content": "• Provided hands-on support during high-pressure delivery phases, ensuring deadlines were met without compromising quality.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "cv79d7u",
                  "name": "role",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 6,
                  "padding": [
                    16,
                    0,
                    0,
                    0
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv74EQk",
                      "fill": "#111827",
                      "content": "Sky — Senior Developer",
                      "fontFamily": "Lexend",
                      "fontSize": 18,
                      "fontWeight": "semibold"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv75uVZ",
                      "fill": "#6B7280",
                      "content": "Sep 2020 – Apr 2021",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv76kKA",
                      "fill": "#4B5563",
                      "content": "• Delivered key features for the replatformed CRM front end supporting Sky Glass & Stream.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv773hA",
                      "fill": "#4B5563",
                      "content": "• Identified architectural gaps and proposed pragmatic solutions to improve performance, maintainability, and security.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv78Q5l",
                      "fill": "#4B5563",
                      "content": "• Mentored mid-level and junior engineers, supporting their progression to senior roles.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "cv86PeW",
                  "name": "role",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 6,
                  "padding": [
                    16,
                    0,
                    0,
                    0
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv808hp",
                      "fill": "#111827",
                      "content": "Sky — JavaScript Developer",
                      "fontFamily": "Lexend",
                      "fontSize": 18,
                      "fontWeight": "semibold"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
