                      "content": "Oct 2015 – Sep 2020",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv229Ftt",
                      "fill": "#D1D5DB",
                      "content": "• Maintained and evolved Sky's customer chat platform, including multiple Node.js services and front-end applications.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv230nBf",
                      "fill": "#D1D5DB",
                      "content": "• Built real-time data solutions to improve chat pacing accuracy.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv2311SM",
                      "fill": "#D1D5DB",
                      "content": "• Supported numerous teams integrating chat functionality across sky.com.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cv232Wmd",
                      "fill": "#D1D5DB",
                      "content": "• Provided out-of-hours production support as sole long-term maintainer of the chat solution.",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
